ding longshort equities event driven and relative value strategies to its clients it was founded in  and is based in new york city with an addition office in new york wafra investment advisory group inc operates as a subsidiary of wafra intervest corporation detailed description  park avenuest floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwwafracom key executives for wafra investment advisory group inc mr fawaz almubaraki chief investment officer ceo director headevp of alternative investments ms jeanine macfadyen cpa corporate finance  cfo mr vincent paul campagna chief compliance officer coo executive vp  director mr robert w toan jd head of structured finance division mr p christopher leary senior vice president of the securities division and fixed income strategist compensation as of fiscal year  wafra investment advisory group inc key developments wafra investment advisory group inc presents at th annual european pensions symposium feb  pm jan   wafra investment advisory group inc presents at th annual european pensions symposium feb  pm venue parco dei principi hotel rome italy speakers ghazi alhajeri managing director of investments and portfolio manager in the alternative investments division similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target mergeracquisition june   the milagro coral gables apartment complex in florida fund raising may   omers ventures fund iii mergeracquisition november   the ritzcarlton kapalua resort request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at lea